                    SimCity V1.07 NOTICES:
Installing new version (if this is an upgrade):
	You must rerun the install program in order to update the version of
SimCity that you are using.

CURSOR CONTROL:
   With the PS/2 & BUS type mouse interfaces, the keyboard mouse-emulation
has been disabled.

COVOX CARD and the PS/2 MOUSE:
   If you are using a PS/2 type mouse interface, you cannot use the COVOX card
with SimCity.

TERRAIN EDITOR:
   If you order the TERRAIN EDITOR, please make sure you specify which size
disk you require.

NEW:
   Now available is a hi-res 640 x 480 monochrome MCGA/VGA display mode and
a low-res 320 x 200 256 color MCGA/VGA display mode. Also, you now can exit
from the introduction screen (the city sign) by pressing <ctrl><X>.
